{"tid":799874,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸歷程 - 持續更新","createTime":"2018-08-30T12:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T02:02:26.000Z","uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6db82c93c626931a19d3ebbffed5a27c78cf0371","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"我生左暗瘡5年<br />\n唔算好嚴重但永遠keep住至少兩三粒<br />\n返風落雨又一堆咁<br />\n<br />\n7月3日的起心肝開始A酸療程<br />\n醫生開40mg比我，食Reducar<br />\n食左三星期冇乜爆發冇再生，之後我on99走去買Orbis隻物理防曬，貪佢唔洗好似化學防曬咁補搽同埋有少少粉底效果。<br />\n點知呢個就係惡夢開始。<br />\n即刻開始生返，用另一隻Paula Choice物防情況一樣<br />\n但我又日日要見人，彷彿對d防曬既粉底效果著左迷一樣照用，咁就形成左個惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n去到而家已經差不多兩星期，雖然收哂油，但因為隻防曬我情況冇乜好轉。<br />\n點解我可以肯定係隻防曬問題？因為我冇用一星期都冇生過，今日一用即生。<br />\n<br />\n今日開始決定唔用個隻防曬<br />\n唉但又唔捨得佢有少少粉底既功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇絲打有不致痘粉底介紹<br />\n我係巴打但要見人令我想化妝<br />\n我知我好On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個Post會持續更新我既進度<br />\n大家同路人都可以起到分享下，無任歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def7ff192c58c4ba555e9ca92799a6c7e7746ae3","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"勸同路人唔好用物理防曬"},{"pid":"415473ff11a17a2039515ea342b5f25997f52419","tid":799874,"uid":138744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"用雅漾果隻30spf pa+++ 一個台灣皮膚專科醫生推介"},{"pid":"2d2c8198a64b57108a7df2354487902fe7886bd3","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用雅漾果隻30spf pa+++ 一個台灣皮膚專科醫生推介</blockquote><br />\n係，我都諗住買呢隻<br />\n不過佢冇潤色功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65a59f5595482e424bd5144020c911265513c35","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"我真係好on9<br />\n明知自己男人老狗仲要咁既情況最唔應該化妝<br />\n但自己真係接受唔到塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ff448449acf06c23eba061c896e858187a00d","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"好後悔點解唔早d食"},{"pid":"418f1327567523b1cfe0f206b74bc9369cddd7b5","tid":799874,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"咁既垃圾毒藥都啱"},{"pid":"e6bb747e7adaded7d151431655bc6dcc3e86f50d","tid":799874,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"A酸打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53a75286e361d4cf63e63942e4460faac61204f","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c731dd720ac2da51b1984888c4d2b00ec761c3d","tid":799874,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"Puggg"},{"pid":"9d8835d1a730a89346c1ca740538f8b150ea2da9","tid":799874,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"樓主而家好返未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}